  <heading>MOVS (unpredicated)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Move predicate (unpredicated), setting the condition flags</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction reads all elements from the source predicate and places those elements in the
destination predicate.
This instruction is unpredicated. This instruction sets the First (N), None (Z), and !Last (C)
condition flags based on the predicate result,
and sets the V flag to zero.</para>
    </authored>
    <affected_by_sme output="NZCV condition flags"/>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
  <operationalnotes/>
